thread.title: Washington's federal fugitives

author: LEVI PULKKINEN, SEATTLEPI.COM STAFF
title: Washington's federal fugitives
text:
Federal agents are looking for dozens of suspects with connections to Washington.
Their alleged crimes range from fraud to child pornography to murder to environmental crimes. Click through the gallery above for a look at them.
Sources for the images here include the U.S. Marshals Service, Interpol, the FBI and other federal law enforcement agencies.
Some of the men and women pictured above have not been convicted of the crimes they’re accused of. Others absconded after they were convicted.
Click through for a look at violent fugitives sought by the state Department of Corrections . The state’s missing sex offenders can be found here .
